# DomusCoins-SmartContract
DomusCoins Smart Contracts

npm install -g truffle

truffle develop

compile

migrate


DomusCoins Smart Contracts steup

-change all address(Board address and admin address)

-Create token contract (DOCToken contract)

-Set pretoken defult price ether TOKEN_PER_TOKEN varible in DOCTokenSaleConfig contract

-ICO sale contract create( DOCTokenSale contract)

-In ICO contract call funcation initilize SET address DOC token

-In DOC Token contract  set addrees of ICO contract in setICOAddress funcation

-Transter 10M token ICO sale contract address

-ICO contract  send 1 ether(As per requriment) and call updateToken per ether funcation.(Update price of  ether every hours)

-Buy token 



#Note

DOCTokenSale contract  Admin can start and stop ICO.
function resume()  // Allows the owner to resume the sale.


